  <name>Connected</name>
  <summary>Phone connectivity applet for the COSMIC desktop</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Connected is a panel applet for the COSMIC desktop environment that provides
    phone-to-desktop connectivity using KDE Connect as a backend.</p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Device battery status and connectivity monitoring</li>
      <li>SMS messaging with conversation threads</li>
      <li>Media player remote control</li>
      <li>Desktop notifications for calls, messages, and file transfers</li>
      <li>Ping your phone to find it</li>
      <li>File sharing between devices</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
